summary: This is a colourful and lively retexture of Tel Mithryns exterior and interior to give a more magical  feel to the great wizard Neloth's home!
descriptionHtml:
[center][color=#6aa84f][size=6]Fantasy Tel Mithyrn[/size][/color][/center]
[center][color=#b6d7a8][size=3]This is a colorful and lively retexture of Tel Mithryns exterior and interior to give a more magical  feel to the great wizards Neloths home! [/size][/color][/center]
[size=3]
[/size][color=#d5a6bd][size=3]For you to get the best look for Fantasy Tel Mithryn to look all green and lush, I highly recommend you download[/size][/color]
[url=http://http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/34570/?]Summer Solstheim HD by Ichibu[/url] 
[url=http://http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/141/?tab=1&navtag=%2Fajax%2Fmoddescription%2F%3Fid%3D141%26preview%3D&pUp=1]Skyrim Flora Overhaul Summer Edition by vurt[/url][color=#93c47d][size=2]

[b]Please Note[/b]
[/size][/color][list]
[*][color=#93c47d][size=2]Textures do not load when looking at Tel Mithryn from a long distance.[/size][/color]
[*][color=#93c47d][size=2]Their is a faint small white seem line crossing the mushrooms when looking at them from a distance.[/size][/color]
[/list]
[color=#9fc5e8][b]Compatibility[/b]
This mod works with everything accept for other mods that also edit the Tel Mithryn textures.
[/color]
[color=#ea9999][b]Tools Used[/b]
NifSkope-1.1.0-rc6
Photoshop CS3
[/color]
author: SiennaGrace
